# Map Rendering Pattern

## Purpose

Render lists of data.

## When To Use

- API lists
- UI collections

## Pattern

```javascript
array.map((item) => <Component key={item.id} />);
```

## Example

```javascript
users.map((user) => <p key={user.id}>{user.name}</p>);
```

## Line-by-Line

- loops through array
- returns JSX per item
- key ensures stable rendering

## Common Mistakes

- missing key
- using index as key

## What Breaks If Done Wrong

- rendering bugs

## Notes

- always use unique key
